\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MyPromptsPath\cf2 \cb1 : The absolute path to the directory where all of your prompt files (both JSON and HTML) are stored. Keyboard Maestro must have this variable set to locate your configurations.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
